---
title: Mexican Chicken Burrito Bowl with Black Bean Rice & Sour Cream
description: This burrito bowl is guaranteed to be a new favourite. Our star Mexican Fiesta spice blend gives the chicken oodles of flavour, while the easy pickled onion, tangy sour cream and fresh tomato salsa tie it all together.
